## Pattern

```gherkin
@Rule(NN)
Rule: [Rule name]

  @Scenario(NN)
  Scenario: [Testable behavior]
    Given [precondition]
    When [action]
    Then [observable outcome]
```

**Note:** This creates binding work — Tesaki will automatically follow up with CreateMissingBindings when new steps are introduced. Do NOT run `namako gate`/`namako lint`/`namako steps`; Tesaki will validate.
